### GCP Deployment

Infra scripts under `infra/gcp`
- `deploy_vm.sh` creates GPU VMs
- `infra/gcp/k8s` contains Kubernetes manifests
- Run `sim_runner.py --use-gpu` for GPU-enabled simulation

